 \frac{n^2}{n-2}\in O(n) 
 \frac{n^2}{n-2} = n+\frac{2n}{n-2} \leq n+2n= 3n \,,
 \frac{n}{n-2}<n\,, \forall n > 2 
\frac{n^2}{n-2}
\frac{n^2 - 4}{n-2} + \frac{4}{n-2} = \frac{(n+2)(n-2)}{n-2} + \frac{4}{n-2} = n + 2 + \frac{4}{n-2} \leq n + 6
n \geq 6
\frac{n^2}{n-2} \leq 2n
\frac{n^2}{n-2} \in O(n)
\,n\to\infty\,
\frac{n^2}{n-2}=\mathcal O(n)\Longleftrightarrow\,\exists\,K\in\Bbb R\;\;s.t.\;\; \left|\frac{\frac{n^2}{n-2}}{n}\right|=\left|\frac{n^2}{n^2-2n}\right|\leq K
\,n\to\infty\,
\,\displaystyle{\frac{n^2}{n^2-2n}\xrightarrow [n\to\infty]{} 1}\,
